# PixelArt AI Provider — Implementation Plan

## Context

The Vercel AI SDK is a monorepo of provider packages that implement standard interfaces (`ImageModelV3`, `LanguageModelV3`, etc.) defined in `@ai-sdk/provider`. This plan adds a new fictional `@ai-sdk/pixelart` package that implements **image generation only** using the `ImageModelV3` interface. The package follows the patterns established by `@ai-sdk/black-forest-labs`, which is the simplest real image-only provider in the repo.

The PixelArt provider will call `https://api.pixelart.ai/v1` and support three provider-specific settings: `style`, `pixelDensity`, and a standard `size`. No text, embedding, or other model types are supported.

---

## Files to Create

All files live under `packages/pixelart/`. No existing files are modified (except the root `tsconfig.json` requires a reference entry — but since the task says "do NOT modify existing provider packages", and the root tsconfig is not a provider package, it should be updated to register the new package for TypeScript project references).

